Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.beans.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Component
 @Entity
public class User
extends Object
implements Serializable
    User class. All users have an id, username, batch, firstname, lastname, email, phone, address, city, state, zip.
